{"tid":2462390,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子涉非法集結被捕 白衫警：你係曱甴唔使搵律師 今裁定罪名成立 還押候判","createTime":"2021-03-26T03:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T03:37:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d7db6bc47e9e8f50489629a4d77b6bbbe0d638f3","tid":2462390,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14639&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=8f58e5aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14639</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第二庭 <br />\n#黃士翔裁判官 #裁決<br />\n#1201旺角 <br />\n#非法集結 #攻擊性武器 #雷射筆<br />\n<br />\n👤呂(32)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 非法集結 <br />\n(2) 管有攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n呂手足被控於2019年12月1日在旺角彌敦道與亞皆老街交界參與非法集結。同日在新填地街453號外的公眾地方管有攻擊性武器，即一支雷射筆。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n速報<br />\n<br />\n特別事項 -- 錄影會面及招認自願性<br />\n法庭裁定被告清楚明白羈留人士通知書內容，並沒有受威逼利誘的情況下自願招認。<br />\n<br />\n控罪1<br />\n罪名成立❗️<br />\n<br />\n控罪2<br />\n罪名不成立❗️<br />\n<br />\n詳情後補....<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年4月15日0930西九龍裁判法院第十四庭，期間以取背景報告及心理醫生報告，還押監房看管。"},{"pid":"1de5f53866a9342154688150acd5ff759347a521","tid":2462390,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae306823f61e93727dcdd1187a2d33456fe307d8","tid":2462390,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8dd475138257c82e35a6d84034071a19605349","tid":2462390,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e51df2190f76bfae63c0097fa28f8682333d2a","tid":2462390,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:33:33.000Z","msg":"前年12月有示威者在旺角一帶聚集堵路，並用雷射筆射向警方防線。32歲地盤散工被控當日參與非法集結及藏有攻擊性武器，今於西九龍裁判法院受審。辯方指被告在拘留期間，警方無視他要求會見律師，有白衫警更謂：「你係曱甴，唔使搵律師。」又有警員誘使被告錄下招認供詞。惟作供警員不同意指控。<br />\n<br />\n警員23503供稱，前年11月30日晚上在彌敦道乘車巡邏期間，聽到有人向警車投擲雜物的聲音，下車查看發現近旺角道出口有約250至300名示威者追出，向警方投擲傘、水樽及汽油彈，警方兩次發射催淚煙驅散。至凌晨1時許，警員再到彌敦道近弼街掃蕩，約百名示威者集結、叫口號及堵路，警方曾舉藍旗及作出口頭警告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師反對控方兩段呈堂錄影，內含為被告疑在誘使下作出的招認內容。辯方指出，被告在羈留室曾兩次向警員16698提出要求見律師及家人，均遭無視，一名白衫警更向被告表示「你係曱甴，唔使搵律師」。"},{"pid":"ed8c425417f33a8b7bb4ec6b42bd863687f02a27","tid":2462390,"uid":223198,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"法治 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65edfb54742d05004a32b9b379dfac444de9cf1d","tid":2462390,"uid":71092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:34:22.000Z","msg":"嘩 好公平公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a929d63d4a641eedc759f2891ad24736d707874","tid":2462390,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c337e13118c45db96450ced11fda435ba55dc51f","tid":2462390,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece25c74d72cc62c4eda13c452bf32b130ddc1a5","tid":2462390,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"心理醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}